Installation:

    git clone https://github.com/KKuryllo/vim.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

    for vim support:
    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc

    for tmux support:
    ln -s ~/.vim/tmux.conf ~/.tmux.conf

    for neovim support:
    # basically you want a .config directory without a nvim inside
    rm -rf ~/.config/nvim
    mkdir -p ~/.config

    ln -s ~/.vim ~/.config/nvim
    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.config/nvim/init.vim

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update

Install the_silver_searcher for use with ack.vim

https://github.com/ggreer/the_silver_searcher

